#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:14
msgid ""
"The ruler is an interactive tool where you can drag lines in the scene to "
"measure distances or angles. Optionally snapping to geometry could be activated "
"for better accuracy or to measure wall thickness. The ruler can be accessed "
"from the Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"标尺是一种交互式工具，可以在场景中拖动线条来测量距离或角度。 可选地，可以激活对"
"几何体的吸附以获得更好的精度或来测量墙壁厚度。 可以从工具栏访问标尺。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:20
msgid "Example of the ruler and protractor."
msgstr "标尺和量角器的示例。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:24
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用法"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:26
msgid "Here are common steps for using the ruler:"
msgstr "以下是使用标尺的常用步骤："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:28
msgid "Activate the Ruler from the Toolbar."
msgstr "从工具栏激活标尺。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click and drag in the viewport to define the initial start/end point for the "
"ruler."
msgstr "在视图中单击并拖动以定义标尺的初始开始/结束点。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:30
msgid ""
"Orbit the view and click on either end of the ruler to re-position it. Holding :"
"kbd:`Ctrl` enables snap to elements."
msgstr "视轨视图并单击标尺的任一端以重新定位它。 按住 :kbd:`Ctrl` 可以吸附元素。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:32
msgid "Click on the middle to measure angles."
msgstr "单击中间以测量角度。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:33
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`Return` to store the ruler for later use or :kbd:`Esc` to cancel."
msgstr "按 :kbd:`Return` 存储标尺供以后使用或 :kbd:`Esc` 取消。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:37
msgid ""
"Editing operations can be used while the ruler is running, however, tools like "
"the knife cannot be used at the same time."
msgstr "标尺运行时可以使用编辑操作，但是刀具等工具不能同时使用。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:42
msgid "Unit settings and scale from the scene are used for displaying dimensions."
msgstr "场景中的单位设置和缩放用于显示尺寸。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:46
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:48
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` Adds new ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` 添加新标尺。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:49
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` Drag end points to place them, hold :kbd:`Ctrl` to snap, hold :kbd:"
"`Shift` to measure thickness."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`LMB` 拖动终点放置它们，按住 :kbd:`Ctrl` 吸附，按住 :kbd:`Shift` 来测量厚"
"度。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:50
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` Drag the center point to measure angles, drag out of the view to "
"convert back to a ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`LMB` 拖动中心点测量角度，拖出视图转换回标尺。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:51
msgid ":kbd:`Delete` Deletes the ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`Delete` 删除标尺。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:52
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-C` Copies the rulers value to the clipboard."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-C` 将标尺值复制到剪贴板。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:53
msgid ":kbd:`Esc` Exit tool."
msgstr ":kbd:`Esc` 退出工具。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:54
msgid ":kbd:`Return` Saves the rulers for the next time the tool is activated."
msgstr ":kbd:`Return` 保存标尺供下次激活工具时使用。"
